164
00:07:19,830 --> 00:07:20,740
Dad, Mum,

165
00:07:21,591 --> 00:07:23,431
I've decided to bring
Xin Zheng's parents

166
00:07:23,431 --> 00:07:24,390
here.

167
00:07:24,991 --> 00:07:25,950
I'll bring Tou Tou here too.

168
00:07:28,234 --> 00:07:29,146
Ling Lan,

169
00:07:30,311 --> 00:07:31,790
I support your decision.

170
00:07:35,390 --> 00:07:36,270
I will arrange Tou Tou

171
00:07:36,270 --> 00:07:37,631
to pick up Grandpa and Granny in Yunnan.

172
00:07:38,080 --> 00:07:38,950
