173
00:07:39,110 --> 00:07:40,110
I'll head to the medical centre

174
00:07:40,591 --> 00:07:41,450
and prepare to close it down.

175
00:07:43,151 --> 00:07:44,031
I'll check on

176
00:07:44,270 --> 00:07:45,431
Shan Dao too.

177
00:07:45,550 --> 00:07:46,911
