278
00:11:07,951 --> 00:11:10,710
As long as they pull through
the most dangerous moments

279
00:11:10,710 --> 00:11:12,751
and let their immunity grow,

280
00:11:13,271 --> 00:11:14,470
their bodies

281
00:11:14,710 --> 00:11:15,751
will recover naturally.

282
00:11:16,350 --> 00:11:17,271
That's right.

